# Design System Starter Kit — Windsurf Rules

> **Start here:** `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` contains the full architectural context —
> design principles, layer model, token system, prefix mechanics, Figma integration,
> build chain, and decision log. Read it first for the "why" behind these rules.

## Project Context

Multi-framework design system monorepo (React + Vue + Svelte + HTML/CSS) with a **CSS-first base layer**. All visual styles live in `packages/css-components/` as BEM SCSS. Framework packages are thin wrappers. Design tokens built via Style Dictionary. Target: WCAG 2.2 AA.

## Architecture

```
@ds/tokens → @ds/css-components → @ds/react / @ds/vue / @ds/svelte / @ds/html
```


## Configurable Prefix

Defined in `/ds.config.json` (default: `vcds`). Change: `node scripts/set-prefix.js <new-prefix>` then `pnpm build`.
CSS vars: `--vcds-*`. BEM classes: `.vcds-*`. JS: `DS_PREFIX` from `@ds/shared/prefix`.

## Critical Rules

1. **CSS-first** — ALL component styles go in `packages/css-components/src/components/`. Framework wrappers MUST NOT contain `<style>` blocks or CSS Modules.
2. **BEM naming** — `.{prefix}-{component}`, `.{prefix}-{component}--{variant}`, `.{prefix}-{component}__{element}`.
3. **Tokens over hardcoded values** — ALWAYS use `var(--vcds-{category}-{name})` in SCSS. Never hardcode colors, spacing, or typography.
4. **Semantic tokens only** — Components reference semantic tokens (e.g., `color-action-primary`), never primitives (e.g., `blue-500`).
5. **Accessibility first** — Every interactive component needs keyboard handling, ARIA attributes, visible focus indicators, and axe-core tests.
6. **Blueprint-driven** — Start with `/blueprints/scss/` for SCSS, then `/blueprints/{framework}/` for wrappers.

## Creating a Component — Order Matters

1. SCSS → `packages/css-components/src/components/_name.scss` (BEM, tokens only)
2. Register → Add `@use 'components/name';` to `src/index.scss`
3. Build → `pnpm --filter @ds/css-components build`
4. HTML → `packages/html/examples/name.html` (reference markup)
5. Wrappers → React, Vue, Svelte (props → BEM classes, NO styles)
6. Tests + Stories

## Framework Patterns

- **React**: forwardRef, string class names (`'{prefix}-button vcds-button--primary'`), NO CSS Modules
- **Vue**: `<script setup lang="ts">`, array class binding, NO scoped styles, `Ds` prefix
- **Svelte**: Svelte 5 runes (`$props()`), `class:` directives, NO `<style>` block

## Key Commands

```
pnpm build                                # Build all (tokens → CSS → frameworks)
pnpm --filter @ds/tokens build            # Build tokens
pnpm --filter @ds/css-components build    # Build component CSS
pnpm --filter @ds/docs dev               # Start Storybook
pnpm test                                # Run all tests
pnpm changeset                           # Version changes
```

